    <Placemark>
      <name>Veronica Ryan Retrospective</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>Veronica Ryan Retrospective</b><br><i>Arts &amp; Culture</i><br>Mon 30th Mar – Sun 14th Jun<br>Whitechapel Gallery, Whitechapel<br>Check site<br><br>Explore one of the biggest presentations of work by Turner Prize-winning artist Veronica Ryan, known for her thought-provoking sculptures and installations.<br><br><a href="https://www.timeout.com/london/things-to-do/things-to-do-in-london-this-week">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
