      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Jaja’s African Hair Braiding</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>Jaja’s African Hair Braiding</b><br><i>Theatre</i><br>Mon 30th Mar – Sat 25th Apr<br>Hammersmith<br>Check site<br><br>A dynamic play set in a West African hair salon in Harlem, offering a glimpse into the lives and stories of its characters over a single working day.<br><br><a href="https://www.timeout.com/london/things-to-do/things-to-do-in-london-this-week">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
