      <description><![CDATA[<b>Welcome to Pemfort</b><br><i>Theatre</i><br>Mon 30th Mar – Sat 18th Apr<br>Soho<br>Check site<br><br>A small-town drama that begins as a cosy comedy about eccentrics staging a fundraiser, but takes unexpected turns with the arrival of an ex-con.<br><br><a href="https://www.timeout.com/london/things-to-do/things-to-do-in-london-this-week">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
